1. *Poruke* su bile jako važne za moj život (The messages were very important for my life). 
2. Ona je uputila svoje *poruke* preko mobilnog telefona (She sent her messages via mobile phone). 
3. Svi smo zadovoljni njegovim *porukama* (We are all pleased with his messages). 
4. Oni su primali *poruke* sa svojim dugogodišnjim prijateljima (They were receiving messages from their long-time friends). 
5. Ona je odgovorila na sve *poruke* (She answered all the messages). 
6. Ona je poslala svoje *poruke* preko interneta (She sent her messages via internet).